room_title: Escape room "Zombie Autopsy" by Gulf Coast Escape Room in Orange Beach
room_address: 701 Gulf Shores Parkway Gulf Shores, AL 36542
room_description: The virus is quickly spreading all around the world. You are trapped in a lab that was used to autopsy zombies to synthesize a cure for the zombie plague. Find the origin of the virus, discover the truth and try to stay alive before your time is up and the disease is unstoppable.
